8d737504bef976ed4d82b2ade","tid":1830622,"uid":13544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:12:54.000Z","msg":"意念好好 但配色可以再搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />74X睇到眼殘<br />\n同埋72A寧寧舍舍凸咗出嚟可以再標返清楚啲"},{"pid":"7b464321173a9ba639e1e1c1e2977dfaa9d3514e","tid":1830622,"uid":204856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:15:02.000Z","msg":"大埔人留下正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1695edda0e368aad4b24b0c0578fb52a9c1e9f","tid":1830622,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:15:59.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c9db260dc664b89787eee39ca973c7abcc7b2775","tid":1830622,"uid":127735,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:16:25.000Z","msg":"真心，如果有人整曬18區巴士路線圖，再整番個手機App方便搵路線<br />\n完全係可以置黨鐵於外太空<br />\n樓主好好，只要傳開去同埋等人知道有持續更新，一定會愈黎愈多人用，原理同黃色經濟圈一樣<br />\n<br />\n召喚巴膠同手機達人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897d5ddf91b823ebc2a686e5797b4b1743887c8e","tid":1830622,"uid":35445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:18:07.000Z","msg":"少少諗法<br />\n<br />\n首先係睇落有啲花，不過我都諗唔到點改善住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路線上<br />\n大埔去港島仲可以考慮 74x / 75x / 307 &gt; 680 681 682 @ 大老山 / 東隧（307) 做駁腳，咁就可以cover埋北角到灣仔一帶 (我見圖無包括680 681) <br />\n<br />\n東隧可以加埋694，柴灣人愛車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n落港島另一條路線可以係 271 &gt; 紅隧巴 (e.g 118) @ 加士居道 / 75x &gt; 紅隧巴@mk <br />\n<br />\n巴打加油！欣賞你嘅做法"},{"pid":"a0ecb7f6edf1c082e49936042a9f515e9d47a586","tid":1830622,"uid":54514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"75X去程都經樂富喎<br />\n同埋港島區可以東隧轉680 619等等去北角至銅鑼灣一段"},{"pid":"c1914f392761015cceabb77bd9